%N A385970 a(n) is the minimum number of powers needed to obtain the n-th term of sequence A385969.
%C A385970 The sequence is unbounded (conjectured).
%H A385970 Alberto Zanoni, <a href="https://be-numbers.jimdosite.com">BE-numbers</a>
%H A385970 A. Zanoni and M. Zanoni, <a href="https://www.anstuocmath.ro/mathematics/anale2026v2/10_ZanoniAlberto_et_all.pdf">Sums of bases-exponents positive integer powers</a>, Analele ştiinţifice ale Universităţii "Ovidius" Constanţa, 34-2 (2026), 197-210.
%e A385970 a(1) = 1, as  4 = 2^2
%e A385970 a(2) = 2, as 17 = 2^3 + 3^2
%e A385970 a(3) = 1, as 27 = 3^3
%e A385970 a(4) = 2, as 31 = 2^2 + 3^3
%e A385970 a(7) = 3, as 59 = 2^4 + 3^3 + 4^2
